			<!-- / icon and title -->
		
		
		<!-- message -->
		<div>The idea for all classes to solo is great, but in reality most classes already can. having our aggro's pop faster and with less drain on edurance does not help in soloing.<br />
Honestly i think the people at eq dont know what to do with warriors at all. Im sick of the fact that i have Vadds armour, and high end gear above Qvic and still cannot solo any mobs. Even after soloing a light blue i have a choice of 10 minutes bandaging down time or run my heal disc that drains my endurance.<br />
For any chance of warriors being able to solo we need do be able to do more damage. I agree with the previouse post about sk and pallys out damaging us. Why is is a pallys and sk can get the same level of ac, hp and leach and heal hp. If your going to implement the idea of potions makes them restricted to certain classes.<br />
One good asset of lowering edurance cost on discs is that they can help in soloing, alls you have to do now is lower the waiting time on damage discs.<br />
Maybe we should think outside the box. instead of changes to classes for soloing, why not designate a new zone just for soloing. where all mobs are blue to your level and all the class changes are implemtent withing that zone.<br />
just an idea.<br />
cant wait to see what you come up with.</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
		
		
	
	</td>
</tr>
